Did you know that starting your morning with a high protein breakfast will prevent you from feeling tired after a couple hours and will keep you full for longer? These pancakes have 33 gr of protein! My goal is at least 30gr per meal for blood sugar balance🤝🏽
•
(High protein, gluten free breakfast)
•
👇🏽✨Hemp Protein Pancakes✨
•
ɪɴɢʀᴇᴅɪᴇɴᴛꜱ:
✰4 tbsp (30gr) hemp protein (27 gr protein content) @evohemp
✰Cinnamon
✰1 tbsp monk fruit or coconut sugar
✰1 egg
✰¼ cup nondairy milk
✰3 tbsp oat flour (GF if needed)
✰Add your favorite toppings, I used pistachio butter & cacao nibs!
•
ᴘʀᴇᴘᴀʀᴀᴛɪᴏɴ:
•In a bowl, mix all ingredients. Then heat a small sauce pan w some avocado oil.
•Pour mixture and cook for 3-4 minutes over medium/low heat on both sides, or until pancakes are cooked through.
•Enjoy with your fave toppings!😋
